Permission: com.google.android.c2dm.permission.SEND
[android:exported=true]
manifest_analysis.desc: A Broadcast Receiver is found to be shared with other apps on the device therefore leaving it accessible to any other application on the device. playstore_details.title: CoinCorner – Buy & sell bitcoin. Crypto Wallet
playstore_details.description:
CoinCorner: A Bitcoin exchange and wallet provider helping people to buy Bitcoin quickly, easily and from a trusted place.

We're one of the UK's leading cryptocurrency exchanges, supporting 150,000+ customers in more than 45 countries. The CoinCorner app lets you access your account and portfolio on the go, giving you the ability to buy, sell, send and receive bitcoin wherever you are and whenever you want. 

What features are available?

DEPOSIT WITH CREDIT / DEBIT CARD
Add GBP or EUR funds with your credit or debit card, and buy Bitcoin in minutes. 

BUY AND SELL BITCOIN 
With a simple and clean look, the app makes buying Bitcoin easier than ever before. Want to cash in? You can sell your Bitcoin as easily as you bought it - head to the Buy & Sell page.

SEND AND RECEIVE BITCOIN
Need to make payments on the go? Whoever you're paying, instantly send bitcoin to their bitcoin address. 

Expecting a bitcoin payment? Share your bitcoin address from within the app and receive bitcoin payments without hassle.

SUPPORTED COINS
You can buy and sell Ethereum (ETH), Litecoin (LTC) and Ripple (XRP) in the app too. Please remember that there are no send/receive or withdraw options for these coins yet.

CUSTOMER SUPPORT
If you have a question, please get in touch with our friendly support team on support@coincorner.com and they will be happy to help. (Support is available Monday - Friday, 9:00-5:00pm, GMT)

CoinCorner's mission is to make Bitcoin easy. Cryptocurrencies like Bitcoin are changing the way we think about money - so, wherever you are in your journey, we're here with quick, easy and trusted Bitcoin services.
